A state of unauthorized access of energy
========================================
Every one of us have lack of active state of energy, ie We don't have sufficient energy that keep us in state of healing. Due to lack of active energy within us our senses/ mind/ heart/observation/realization/understanding..so on.. work out with or without our permission. It is the nature of energy to perceive/transform into its higher state using their affinity.

Streaming of structure(changing the structure) is the nature of waves. It is the existence of waves.
Ex-
-Look waves of different movement time to time by a group of people
-Look streaming of flying structure of group of birds
-Look stream of water on their flow
-Look construction of new state of society ie restructure of old society
-Look streaming in your life style

***Energy within you not follow your permission since you get build on top of energy within you only***

Unauthorized access of External source of energy
------------------------------------------------
When you realize some object/energy makes your life some what more stable then you have two option either you buy or steal/snatch.
When you buy, you exchange the same amount of energy that are in some another form/state, how do you feel, little/more good.
It is nothing but authorized access of energy.(-X mixed +X=0)

But when you steal/snatch the object, you feel bad after some time or after use of that object, since at the time of steal/snatch the object hindrance in your state already released same amount of energy.(+X mixed -X=0)
This is nothing but unauthorized access of energy.

In both of the case of authorized access or unauthorized access of external source of energy the resultant become zero only but in case of authorized access one feel good and and in case of unauthorized access one feel bad.

-Forcing/pressurizing/forcefully/steal/exploit/to persecute/demotivating/suppressing/so on..are nothing but unauthorized access of attempt.
-Requesting/Kind request /impressing /motivating /begging /making romantic/ joking/ singing/ respecting/ giving/ distributing/serving..so on are the authorized access of energy.
Authorized access of energy can useful to change your state of energy to higher state and making you feel good where as unauthorized access of energy make you frustrated/ exhausted/tired.

***It is our poor state of understanding that try to use unauthorized access of energy***
***It seems to be we get energy from external source but in fact we get in exchange of energy and their resultant always be zero***

Unauthorized access Internal source of energy
--------------------------------------------------------------
Internal source of energy always exists in high intensity state of streaming and their structure are arranged in such a ways that it sustain your lives.
This energy is in abstract state for us. we need to supply more and more energy to our self to activate this point of energy.
In fact when your state of energy reach near to state of abstract energy then it get accessed automatically and it expand.
 
Before and after access of internal source of energy, energy within us is not get changed but the state of energy get changed to higher state.

***Each and every game played by energy only but mass/object come in picture as representative***

